## Variables
# @no-cookie-jar
@user_id = 1
@plan_id = 1
@title = 유저 1 테스트
@title2 = 유저 1 테스트 - 플랜 수정 테스트
@name = 하이요2
@nickname = 하이요24

### 로그인
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("Authorization", response.headers.valueOf("Authorization"));
  client.log("Authorization: " + response.headers.valueOf("Authorization"));

  client.global.set("RefreshToken", response.headers.valueOf("RefreshToken"));
  client.log("RefreshToken: " + response.headers.valueOf("RefreshToken"));
%}

### 플랜 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/plans
Authorization: {{Authorization}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "{{title}}"
}

### 플랜 수정
PATCH http://localhost:8080/v1/plans/{{plan_id}}
Authorization: {{Authorization}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "{{title2}}"
}


### 플랜 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/v1/plans/{{plan_id}}
Authorization: {{Authorization}}
Content-Type: application/json


### 플랜 전체 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/plans?userId={{user_id}}
Authorization: {{Authorization}}
Content-Type: application/json


### 플랜 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/plans/{{plan_id}}
Authorization: {{Authorization}}
Content-Type: application/json


### 플랜Id로 플랜에 있는 카드 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/plans/{{plan_id}}/cards
Authorization: {{Authorization}}
Content-Type: application/json